snippet.title: Pinball Parlor trailer #1 English version
snippet.description:
Mindware will publish Pinball Parlor.
Here is English version trailer #1.

We are waiting for pass steam Greenlight.
Let's vote up thumb !

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles...

* In the trailer(PV) and screenshots, we focused on flippers behaivor during the test, so their rubbers are red instead of white.
